| 2 What is 'cal3d_milk_exporter'?                                            |
o-----------------------------------------------------------------------------o

  Cal3D milk exporter is an exporter plugin for MilkShape 3D that exports
  skeletal based character models and their animations into Cal3D files.


o-----------------------------------------------------------------------------o
| 3 Website                                                                   |
o-----------------------------------------------------------------------------o

  The official website of Cal3D can be found at: http://gna.org/projects/cal3d/


